<li id="cite_note-Jacobs-5"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="Rosh_Hashanah#cite_ref-Jacobs_5-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="Rosh_Hashanah#cite_ref-Jacobs_5-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Jacobs, Louis. "Rosh Ha-Shanah." <i>Encyclopaedia Judaica</i>. Ed. Michael Berenbaum and Fred Skolnik. Vol. 17. 2nd ed. Detroit: Macmillan Reference, 2007. 463–466.</span>
